{"tid":767060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗同石硖尾真係狗也不屌","createTime":"2018-08-04T07:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T09:16:42.000Z","uid":185416,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb8d2a09f9b09c7171cb8c8873ec68f6bb8737c","tid":767060,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"1.多廢老，離遠三尺都有啲味，係又臭又酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，日日坐係公園吹水，講野勁大聲<br />\n<br />\n2.多痴線佬/道友/蝻，住石硖尾應該知，一到夜晚，七仔/ok出面一定有道友，痴線佬駐守，深水埗更唔洗講蝻仲多過蟑螂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 多蝗，好多新移民入住，班友冇文化冇知識，特別係住呢區嘅蝗寶寶，一日都黑嘈嘈嘈，屌佢老味<br />\n<br />\n4.多Mk，街童。十歲以下，食煙飲酒，不計其數，呢班人，老左一係變痴綫佬，一係成為廢老，根本係惡性循環<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住呢區嘅拜託，拜託，唔好生仔。試問你啲仔女，細細個就係呢啲環境長大。接觸廢老，認識MK，又點去脫貧。你地可能話有人脫到，做到成功人士。但我可以話變壞，俾環境逼到冇上進心嘅佔8成以上。唔信你可以睇下各大學嘅公屋比率有幾低。  我自己有幸算入到所謂大學，入面嘅人同自己根本上溝通唔到。佢地有車有樓，日日傾去邊玩/去旅行/咩名車/食洋女。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而自己就繼續係惡性循環入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌我老母，窮就唔好生仔啦，仲要住深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db0773f6665bf8cdccacb9b32dc6aa7d3513000","tid":767060,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"前世做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1238fafab3ecbc3f2ed71153209f9d101be980","tid":767060,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"南山村白田村算不算石硤尾"},{"pid":"d9319430dd242b54ce1dd62a8ea3d9840559d716","tid":767060,"uid":5419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"南昌街公園先恐怖，日光日白道友多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191a64d1a143355000a09b057c95d114957aa430","tid":767060,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"深水埗公園都係廢老專用"},{"pid":"d3528ac2ecb99325d101597b24bfff09c050df75","tid":767060,"uid":197921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"有屋你住已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d04c2a4d96e07043fb2e5c54548361ebf36247e","tid":767060,"uid":147754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a1238fafab3ecbc3f2ed71153209f9d101be980","tid":767060,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"南山村白田村算不算石硤尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"算 好多廢老mk"}]}